Description: 
        pyhector
        --------
        
        Python wrapper for the `Hector simple climate model
        <https://github.com/JGCRI/hector>`_.
        
        **Install** using ::
        
            pip install pyhector
        
        Find **usage** instructions in the `repository
        <https://github.com/openclimatedata/pyhector>`_.
        
        
